Please contact us at support@javisco.vn If you got any problems.

Javis Home offers the most comprehensive voice controlled smart home experience with Alexa. Control your home lighting and other devices hands free. 

Here’s a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "Javis Home" app from Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Register the smart home devices such as JAVIS switch or Home assistant with “Javis Home” app;
(4). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(5). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Javis Home";
(7). Click Enable skill of "Javis Home", then input your account username, password which you already registered via Javis Home
(8). Talk to Echo "“Alexa, discover devices.”. Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands Javis Home has:

Lights:
* Alexa, turn on my living room light
* Alexa, turn off my living room light

Plugs:
* Alexa, turn on my plug
* Alexa, turn off my plug
